Notable changes from upstream Theatre.js
----------------------------------------
  - Renamed the npm scope from @theatre/* to @encorejs/* (and the unscoped
    `theatric` package to @encorejs/tweak).
  - Support for React 19 and react-three-fiber v9.
  - Removed the hosted-cloud update checker and defaulted the studio backend
    to localhost, so the editor does not contact any third-party server.

